അക്കൗണ്ടിങ് മേഖലയില്‍ ഒരു കരിയര്‍ സ്വപ്‌നം കാണുന്നവര്‍ക്ക് ആത്മവിശ്വാസത്തോടെ തെരഞ്ഞെടുക്കാവുന്ന, കൊമേഴ്‌സ് മേഖലയിലെ ഏറ്റവും മികച്ച പ്രൊഫഷണല്‍ കോഴ്‌സുകളിലൊന്നായ ACCA ഇനി മുതല്‍ Entriയിലും. ചിട്ടയായ പഠനവും കൃത്യമായ ഗൈഡന്‍സും ഉറപ്പാക്കുന്ന ENTRI ACCA യ്‌ക്കൊപ്പം കൊമേഴ്‌സിലെ ഭാവി സാധ്യതകള്‍ പഠിക്കാം. സ്വപ്‌നജോലിയിലേക്ക് അല്‍പ്പം നേരത്തെ എത്താന്‍ ഇപ്പോഴേ തയ്യാറായി ഇരുന്നോളൂ!

snippet.title: Kaffara Episode 58 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 21st September 2024
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Kaffara Episode 58 - [Eng Sub] - Ali Ansari - Laiba Khan - Zoya Nasir - 21st September 2024 - HAR PAL GEO

Sitara, a lively orphan living with her brother, aunt, and uncle, finds joy in life's small things despite her aunt's poor treatment. Her aunt keeps her around because she has a share in the family's property.
Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she’s not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation 
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi 
Director: Muhammad Iftikhar Iffi

Salar, the son of a wealthy businessman, is passionate about photography, which often earns him criticism from his family. With a pure heart, Salar is known for evading his responsibilities.
At her cousin's wedding, Sitara wrongly assumes Salar is the photographer. Salar develops a soft spot for Sitara after seeing how poorly she is treated. However, due to a conspiracy, objections arise about their closeness. Salar, once again, avoids the issue, leaving Sitara to face doubts from her own family.
Can Sitara prove she’s not guilty? Will Salar help her avoid further mistreatment? Will her family support Sitara? Can Salar show he genuinely cares? Will there be more plots against Sitara?

snippet.description:
Filmymoji  Middle Class Madhu Kurra Thanam Ganesh Master Episode 03 MCM
"In this Filmymoji Middle Class Madhu episode, Madhu and Mahesh Komali dance to the song 'Love Pandu' in their college. Later, as volunteers, Madhu and Mahesh tell Balli that the college management has asked them to conduct a program the next day. On the same night, Madhu and his friends tell Ganesh Master that they're ready to discontinue their studies. Ganesh Master advises them with kind words. Meanwhile, seniors Kishore and his gang plan to attack Madhu and his friends while they're sleeping, leading to some thrilling and comedic moments. This episode is filled with comedy and emotions."

Jaan Nisar Episode 55 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Danish Taimoor - Hiba Bukhari - Haroon Shahid - 21st September 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Jaan Nisar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

7th Sky Entertainment’s mega project, Jaan Nisar, is the most awaited drama serial of the year.
The highly anticipated project marks the return of the successful on-screen couple of Danish Taimoor and Hiba Bukhari in an unforgettable love story that will steal your heart.

Nosherwan Ghaznavi, a wealthy young man, faces a pivotal moment in his life after his brother's death. This tragedy burdens Nosherwan Ghaznavi with numerous responsibilities, which he reluctantly accepts, only to find them later proving detrimental. However, his life takes a transformative turn upon meeting Dua, falling in love with her at first sight, but it places him at a critical juncture with his responsibilities.

Dua, a beautiful girl from a humble background, is raised by her parents alongside her two sisters. Despite her innocence, fate subjects Dua to a string of misfortunes before encountering Nosherwan Ghaznavi. However, their meeting completely changes their lives.

Will Nowsherwan Ghaznavi find love? What challenges will he face in balancing his duties and his love for Dua? Will his responsibilities jeopardize his love for Dua? What past events have shaped Dua's life, and will they resurface to trouble her? Will Dua return Nowsherwan Ghaznavi’s love?

snippet.title: Chess Olympiad 2024 Round 10 | India vs USA (Open), India vs China (Women)
snippet.description:
The Chess Olympiad 2024 is being held in Budapest, Hungary from 11th to the 23rd of September 2024. Team India starts as the 2nd seed behind USA in the open section and as the top seed in the women's section. The Indian team in the open consists of Arjun Erigaisi, D. Gukesh, Praggnanandhaa, Vidit Gujrathi and P. Harikrishna. The women team of India consists of Harika, Vaishali, Divya Deshmukh, Tania Sachdev and Vantika Agrawal. It's 11 rounds of Swiss League with classical time control. Check out the Round 10 pairings below:

Team India (Open) vs USA:

GM D Gukesh (2764) vs GM Fabiano Caruana (2798)
GM Wesley So (2752) vs GM Rameshbabu Praggnanandhaa (2750)
GM Arjun Erigaisi (2778) vs GM Leinier Dominguez Perez (2748)
GM Levon Aronian (2729) vs GM Vidit Gujrathi (2720)

Team India (Women) vs China:

GM Harika Dronavalli (2502) vs GM Zhu Jiner (2487)
IM Guo Qi (2367) vs GM Vaishali Rameshbabu (2498)
IM Divya Deshmukh (2483) vs WGM Ni Shiqun (2348)
IM Lu Miaoyi (2438) vs IM Vantika Agrawal (2370)

1. Support young Indian talents via HelpChess: https://helpchess.org/

snippet.title: Jayalalithaa கடைசியாகப் பேசியது இதுதான் - Rabi Bernard Interview | Vikatan
snippet.description:
#jayalalitha #sasikala #rabibernard #vikatan 

தொலைக்காட்சி பேட்டியின் முன்னோடியாகத் திகழ்ந்தவர் ரபி பெர்னார்ட். இவர் பல்வேறு அரசியல் தலைவர்கள் முதல் பலரையும் `நேருக்கு நேராக' பேட்டி கண்டிருக்கிறார். அதிமுக ஆட்சிக் காலத்தில் முன்னாள் முதல்வர் ஜெயலலிதாவுக்கு அறிக்கை எழுதுவது, அவருடன் தேர்தல் சுற்றுப்பயணம் மேற்கொள்வது போன்ற பணிகளிலும் இருந்திருக்கிறார். அதிமுக ஆட்சியின்போது நாடாளுமன்ற உறுப்பினராகவும் நியமிக்கப்பட்டார். அவர் விகடனுக்காகக் கொடுத்த ஸ்பெஷல் பேட்டியில், அதிமுக-வின் எதிர்காலம், ஜெயலலிதாவுடன் பயணித்த அனுபவம், அப்பலோ நாட்கள் என அனைத்தும் மனம் திறந்து பேசியுள்ளார் ரவி பெர்னார்ட்.

தொலைக்காட்சி பேட்டியின் முன்னோடியாகத் திகழ்ந்தவர் ரபி பெர்னார்ட். இவர் பல்வேறு அரசியல் தலைவர்கள் முதல் பலரையும் `நேருக்கு நேராக' பேட்டி கண்டிருக்கிறார். அதிமுக ஆட்சிக் காலத்தில் முன்னாள் முதல்வர் ஜெயலலிதாவுக்கு அறிக்கை எழுதுவது, அவருடன் தேர்தல் சுற்றுப்பயணம் மேற்கொள்வது போன்ற பணிகளிலும் இருந்திருக்கிறார். அதிமுக ஆட்சியின்போது நாடாளுமன்ற உறுப்பினராகவும் நியமிக்கப்பட்டார். அவர் விகடனுக்காகக் கொடுத்த ஸ்பெஷல் பேட்டியில், அதிமுக-வின் எதிர்காலம், ஜெயலலிதாவுடன் பயணித்த அனுபவம், அப்பலோ நாட்கள் என அனைத்தும் மனம் திறந்து பேசியுள்ளார் ரவி பெர்னார்ட்.

snippet.title: Squid Game: Season 2 | Special Teaser | Netflix
snippet.description:
The game never stops. Are you ready to play? Squid Game Season 2 arrives December 26, only on Netflix.

More Info on Squid Game Season 2:
Three years after winning Squid Game, Player 456 gave up going to the states and comes back with a new resolution in his mind. Gi-hun once again dives into the mysterious survival game, starting another life-or-death game with new participants gathered to win the prize of 45.6 billion won. Director Hwang Dong-hyuk, who made history at the 74th Primetime Emmys® becoming the first Asian to win Outstanding Directing for a Drama Series, once again helms the series as director, writer, and producer. Lee Jung-jae, Lee Byung-hun, Wi Ha-jun, and Gong Yoo reprise their roles from Season 1 with an impeccable list of new cast members including Yim Si-wan, Kang Ha-neul, Park Gyu-young, Lee Jin-uk, Park Sung-hoon, Yang Dong-geun, Kang Ae-sim, Lee David, Choi Seung-hyun, Roh Jae-won, Jo Yu-ri, and Won Ji-an rounding out the ensemble of colorful characters in the new season.

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81203480

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with 278 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

Squid Game: Season 2 | Special Teaser | Netflix
https://www.youtube.com/@Netflix

Heralding the return of the worldwide hit, a new chapter unfolds as Gi-hun comes back with an agenda, having given up on leaving for the US.

snippet.title: Krushna & Kashmera: Love, Roasts, and Epic Backstage Stories
snippet.description:
Hello Ji, Namaste Dooston Bharti TV Podcast Mein Aapka Fir Se Swagat Hai!

इस Special Episode में हमारे Guest हैं हंसी-मज़ाक से भरी धमाकेदार जोड़ी Krushna Abhishek और Kashmera Shah। इस बार Episode में हम इनके सफर के साथ-साथ, Kashmera को बेहतर तरीके से भी जानेंगे। Laughter Chef से लेकर Bigg Boss तक के अपने Experiences Kashmera इस Episode में खुल कर बयां करेंगी।

वो ये भी बताएंगी कि कैसे Krushna से उनकी मुलाकात हुई और उनके Relationship के पीछे की Beautiful Love Story की भी बहुत सारी बातें होंगी। साथ ही Nach Baliye, Jhalak Dikhla Ja और Comedy Circus जैसे Shows के बारे में भी चर्चा करेंगे। इस Episode में आप Kashmera को As An Entertainer और Krushna की Life Partner के रूप में बेहतर जानेंगे।

Hassi, Pyaar Aur Khulkar Personal Life Ke Baaton Se Bhara Yeh Episode Zaroor Dekhiye, Bharti TV Par!

snippet.title: iPhone 16 Pro MAX Durability Test - Apple tried hard this year...
snippet.description:
Today we durability test the new iPhone 16 Pro Max. Get protection for your iPhone HERE: http://dbrand.com/prism/iphone-16 The new iPhones are always an anticipated smartphone release. This year though - it appears that Apple has hyped up some rather minimal changes, and not even released the bulk of those at launch *cough* Apple Intelligence *cough* Hopefully this helps satisfy any fears of the new iPhone 16 pro max not being durable. Its a solid device. However - I still recommend getting a case. How durable is the iPhone 16 Pro? The answer is here. 

Watch me extract the titanium from the iPhone 15 Pro max here: https://youtu.be/PNLEXAwpCsE?si=cdFUJUbht4hDcHv1

Jaan Nisar Episode 54 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Danish Taimoor - Hiba Bukhari - Haroon Shahid - 20th September 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Jaan Nisar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

7th Sky Entertainment’s mega project, Jaan Nisar, is the most awaited drama serial of the year.
The highly anticipated project marks the return of the successful on-screen couple of Danish Taimoor and Hiba Bukhari in an unforgettable love story that will steal your heart.

Nosherwan Ghaznavi, a wealthy young man, faces a pivotal moment in his life after his brother's death. This tragedy burdens Nosherwan Ghaznavi with numerous responsibilities, which he reluctantly accepts, only to find them later proving detrimental. However, his life takes a transformative turn upon meeting Dua, falling in love with her at first sight, but it places him at a critical juncture with his responsibilities.

Dua, a beautiful girl from a humble background, is raised by her parents alongside her two sisters. Despite her innocence, fate subjects Dua to a string of misfortunes before encountering Nosherwan Ghaznavi. However, their meeting completely changes their lives.

Will Nowsherwan Ghaznavi find love? What challenges will he face in balancing his duties and his love for Dua? Will his responsibilities jeopardize his love for Dua? What past events have shaped Dua's life, and will they resurface to trouble her? Will Dua return Nowsherwan Ghaznavi’s love?

7th Sky Entertainment Presentation

Episode 4196: Ganpati Celebrations Ka Cheque
--------------------------------------------------------
Bhide, Iyer, and Jethalal are thrilled after receiving a cheque worth twenty-one lakhs for Ganpati celebrations, unaware that it's all part of a setup. What unexpected events will unfold next?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - Ep 4196 | 21 Sep 2024
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2024 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #16yearsoftmkoc  #4000episodes

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: दयान ने की चंपा की सिन्दूर मिटाने की कोशिश | Shamshaan Champa | Shemaroo Umang
snippet.description:
Show Synopsis : Shamshaan Champa is a tale of love, supernatural battles, and self-discovery, blending folklore with a powerful, evolving protagonist. In the village of Saguniya, Champa, an innocent 18-year-old girl, is falsely accused of witchcraft by her cruel aunt and uncle. The village, led by the powerful Thakur family, turns against her, resulting in her brutal death. However, her death is not the end but the beginning of her transformation. Three Daayans revive Champa, infusing her with their combined powers. They plan to infiltrate the Thakur family by marrying her off to Vikram, the young Thakur heir. 
 
Show Cast : Trupti Mishra (Champa), Sanchi (Tara), Rakesh Singh (Bhola Chacha), Saurabhi Tiwari (Kamla Chachi), Ayush Shrivastav (Vikram), Rashmi (Kaushalya Devi), Tia Gandwani (Urvashi), Vijay Kumar Singh (Rakesh), Monica Gupta (Madhuri), Inderjeet Modi (Dhruv), Vaishnavi (Rekha), Palak Rana (Pushpa), Mahima Mishra (Shivani), Yash Pal (Akshay), Sandy (Albela), Antara Biswas (Mohini) also known as Mona Lisa, 


शेमारू टीवी लाया है एंटरटेनमेंट आपके पूरे परिवार के लिए। यहाँ देखिये देवों के देव…महादेव, गीत…हुई सबसे परायी, दिल से दी दुआ सौभाग्यवतीभव:, ग्रेट इंडियन लाफ्टर चैलेंज, श…फिर कोई है, माता की चौकी, घर एक सपना, हॉन्टेड नाइट्स और जय जय जय बजरंग बलि जैसे शोज जो आपके परिवार के हर सदस्य को पसंद आएंगे। 

आने वाले एपिसोड्स की जानकारी के लिए हमें फॉलो और सब्सक्राइब करें:
1. https://www.youtube.com/@shemarootv/videos
2. https://www.facebook.com/ShemarooTV
3. https://www.instagram.com/shemaroo.tv

snippet.title: MEN are DYING! Scientists Reveal Men's Y-CHROMOSOME is in DANGER
snippet.description:
Checkout Odoo to simplify your Business - https://www.odoo.com/r/Oum 

Humanity faces a significant threat: according to recent scientific research, men may be on the verge of extinction, with adverse effects on women as well. Recently, you may have heard reports, widely circulated in the news, about a serious illness affecting men at the DNA level, potentially leading to their disappearance.
A recent study from Kansas State University found that the genetic data of the Y chromosome, which is present only in males, is diminishing with each generation. This is alarming! But why is this happening only to men? Why aren’t women experiencing similar changes in their genes? Interestingly, women's DNA is becoming stronger and healthier with each generation. So, does this mean life on Earth could end due to this male-specific decline? Is life fundamentally born with a fatal flaw? Could that flaw be death itself? Let's discuss...

Follow me on Instagram → https://instagram.com/gauravzthakur

snippet.title: Day 3 In Forest...तीसरा दिन सबसे मुश्किल 😭 | 48 Hours Challenge Gone Wrong
snippet.description:
We Spend 48 Hours In Forest.
 
SUBSCRIBE: https://youtube.com/MRINDIANHACKER?sub_confirmation=1

FOLLOW KARLO 😘
Instagram : https://www.instagram.com/dilraj_singh_rawat
Twitter : https://www.x.com/MR_INDIANHACKER
Facebook : https://www.facebook.com/mrindianhacker00
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
𝐅𝐨𝐫 𝐁𝐮𝐬𝐢𝐧𝐞𝐬𝐬 & 𝐂𝐨𝐥𝐥𝐚𝐛𝐨𝐫𝐚𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧'𝐬 𝐂𝐨𝐧𝐭𝐚𝐜𝐭 𝐇𝐞𝐫𝐞:-
Team@mrindianhacker.com
Gaurav@mrindianhacker.com
Manish@mrindianhacker.com
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

"48 Hours in the Forest: A Survival Challenge"

What happens when you're stranded deep in the jungle for 48 hours with no way out? Join us on this incredible journey as we face nature’s toughest challenges: unpredictable rainstorms, no food, and only our survival instincts to guide us. With every passing hour, the struggle to find shelter, stay warm, and keep moving becomes more intense. The forest isn’t just a place of beauty – it’s a test of endurance, patience, and pure willpower.

From building makeshift shelters to finding clean water, and facing the dangers of wild animals, we push ourselves to the limit. Will we survive the full 48 hours? Watch the full video to find out how we overcame nature’s toughest obstacles, or if we finally gave in to the forest.

This is more than just a challenge – it’s a fight for survival.

"48 घंटे जंगल में: एक सर्वाइवल चैलेंज"

क्या होता है जब आप 48 घंटों के लिए गहरे जंगल में फंस जाते हैं, और बाहर निकलने का कोई रास्ता नहीं होता? हमारे साथ इस अद्भुत सफर पर चलें, जहां हम प्रकृति की सबसे कठिन चुनौतियों का सामना कर रहे हैं: अप्रत्याशित बारिश, खाने की कमी, और सिर्फ हमारे सर्वाइवल स्किल्स ही हमारा सहारा हैं। हर गुजरते घंटे के साथ, आश्रय ढूंढने, गर्म रहने, और चलते रहने का संघर्ष और भी कठिन हो जाता है। जंगल सिर्फ एक खूबसूरत जगह नहीं है – यह सहनशक्ति, धैर्य, और इच्छाशक्ति की असली परीक्षा है।

चाहे वह अस्थायी आश्रय बनाना हो, साफ पानी ढूंढना हो, या जंगली जानवरों से बचना हो, हम अपनी हदों को पार कर रहे हैं। क्या हम पूरे 48 घंटे सर्वाइव कर पाएंगे? जानने के लिए पूरा वीडियो देखें, और देखें कैसे हमने प्रकृति की सबसे कठिन चुनौतियों को पार किया, या क्या आखिरकार हमने जंगल के आगे हार मान ली।

यह सिर्फ एक चैलेंज नहीं है – यह जीवन और मौत की लड़ाई है।

What happens when you're stranded deep in the jungle for 48 hours with no way out? Join us on this incredible journey as we face nature’s toughest challenges: unpredictable rainstorms, no food, and only our survival instincts to guide us. With every passing hour, the struggle to find shelter, stay warm, and keep moving becomes more intense. The forest isn’t just a place of beauty – it’s a test of endurance, patience, and pure willpower.

From building makeshift shelters to finding clean water, and facing the dangers of wild animals, we push ourselves to the limit. Will we survive the full 48 hours? Watch the full video to find out how we overcame nature’s toughest obstacles, or if we finally gave in to the forest.

This is more than just a challenge – it’s a fight for survival.

"48 घंटे जंगल में: एक सर्वाइवल चैलेंज"

क्या होता है जब आप 48 घंटों के लिए गहरे जंगल में फंस जाते हैं, और बाहर निकलने का कोई रास्ता नहीं होता? हमारे साथ इस अद्भुत सफर पर चलें, जहां हम प्रकृति की सबसे कठिन चुनौतियों का सामना कर रहे हैं: अप्रत्याशित बारिश, खाने की कमी, और सिर्फ हमारे सर्वाइवल स्किल्स ही हमारा सहारा हैं। हर गुजरते घंटे के साथ, आश्रय ढूंढने, गर्म रहने, और चलते रहने का संघर्ष और भी कठिन हो जाता है। जंगल सिर्फ एक खूबसूरत जगह नहीं है – यह सहनशक्ति, धैर्य, और इच्छाशक्ति की असली परीक्षा है।

चाहे वह अस्थायी आश्रय बनाना हो, साफ पानी ढूंढना हो, या जंगली जानवरों से बचना हो, हम अपनी हदों को पार कर रहे हैं। क्या हम पूरे 48 घंटे सर्वाइव कर पाएंगे? जानने के लिए पूरा वीडियो देखें, और देखें कैसे हमने प्रकृति की सबसे कठिन चुनौतियों को पार किया, या क्या आखिरकार हमने जंगल के आगे हार मान ली।

यह सिर्फ एक चैलेंज नहीं है – यह जीवन और मौत की लड़ाई है।

Show Synopsis : Main Dil Tum Dhadkan is a gripping family drama series that delves into the raw emotions and itense conflicts of its characters set in Mathura, the show explores the complexities of love, betrayal and redemption, revealing secrets as hearts are laid bare. With compelling performances and a heart-wrenching storyline, Main Dil Tum Dhadkan promises to keep viewers on the edge of their seats as they journey through the highs and lows of human emotions 

Show Cast : Radhika Matthukumar (Radhika), Zaheb A. Siddiqui (Keshav), Kavish (Krish), Neelu Vaghela (Rajeshwari Devi), 

In a dramatic twist of fate, Vrinda, a widow, delivers a stillborn, while Keshav's wife Deepika, who is unwilling to keep her baby, abandons her child. Deepika's baby is given to Vrinda, who unknowingly raises him as her own. Seven years later, Vrinda  moves to Mathura with her son, Kanha, and becomes neighbors with Keshav, Kanha's biological father, and Keshav's orthodox mother Rajeshwari. When Keshav uncovers Kanha's true identity, he demands to reclaim his child. However, Vrindaa, who has poured her heart into raising Kanha, is resolute in her refusal to let him go. This clash leaves them at a critical juncture, raising the question of how Vrinda and Keshav will navigate this life-altering conflict.


शेमारू टीवी लाया है एंटरटेनमेंट आपके पूरे परिवार के लिए। यहाँ देखिये देवों के देव…महादेव, गीत…हुई सबसे परायी, दिल से दी दुआ सौभाग्यवतीभव:, ग्रेट इंडियन लाफ्टर चैलेंज, श…फिर कोई है, माता की चौकी, घर एक सपना, हॉन्टेड नाइट्स और जय जय जय बजरंग बलि जैसे शोज जो आपके परिवार के हर सदस्य को पसंद आएंगे।

snippet.title: When Alpha Male & Feminist Girl Are Neighbours | Ft. Kanikka Kapur & Mohit Kumar | RVCJ Media
snippet.description:
You can be a role model by making a difference to blood cancer patients around the world. Register with DKMS-BMST as a potential stem cell donor so you can someday give a patient a second chance at life! 
Register now: https://www.dkms-bmst.org/rvj001

What happens when two childhood lovers, now an Alpha Male and a Feminist Girl, reunite after years apart? Will their different views bring them closer together, or lead to a heated argument?

snippet.title: Chhote Pehelwaano Ko Mila Ek Bada Surprise | @asianpaints  NeoBharat Pragati Ke Rang
snippet.description:
मैं खुद एक पहलवान हूँ और हरियाणा की पहलवानी कम्युनिटी पर मुझे बहुत गर्व है। ये लोग कड़ी मेहनत करते हैं और हमेशा देश के लिए मेडल जीतने और देश को गर्वित करने की कोशिश करते हैं। आज, @asianpaints  नियोभारत के साथ मिलकर, मैं बजरंग अखाड़े को ट्रांसफॉर्म करने के मिशन पर हूँ, ताकि जब यहां बच्चे आएं, तो उन्हें प्रेरणा मिले और वे देश को और भी गर्वित कर सकें।
 

#PragatiKeRang #AsianPaintsNeoBharat #AsianPaints 
#AnkitBaiyanpuria

snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to SET India: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCpEhnqL0y41EpW2TvWAHD7Q?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 85: Dulha Kahan Gaya?
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
While Koel wonders where her groom disappeared, Vedika and Sagar sign a contractual marriage. Soon after, Sagar and Vedika arrive before the others. Later, Sagar's family refuses to accept their marriage. What will Vedika do?

Show Name: Pukaar - Dil Se Dil Tak
Cast: Sumukhi Pendse, Sukhada Khandkekar, Karan Veer Mehra, Vimarsh Roshan, Pankaj Bhatia, Mishika Popat, Mayanshi Verma, Hanish Kaushal, Abhishek Nigam and Sayali Salunkhe
Episode: 85
Producer: Prateek Sharma

#pukaar #setindia  #pukaardilsediltak #newshow #sumukhipendse #mishikapopat

About Pukaar Dil Se Dil Tak
--------------------------
Pukaar Dil Se Dil Tak brings story of a woman and her two daughters are separated from each other due to an evil man's sinister plan. Through the complex web of lies, betrayal, murder and a forbidden romance, can the sisters reunite with each other and their mother to avenge the death of their beloved father and husband? 'Pukaar' stars Sumukhi Pendse, Sukhada Khandkekar, Karan Veer Mehra, Vimarsh Roshan, Pankaj Bhatia, Mishika Popat, Mayanshi Verma, Hanish Kaushal, Abhishek Nigam and Sayali Salunkhe.

snippet.title: How To Go To The Next Level? By Sandeep Maheshwari | Motivational Video Hindi
snippet.description:
Sandeep Maheshwari is a name among millions who struggled, failed and surged ahead in search of success, happiness and contentment. Just like any middle class guy, he too had a bunch of unclear dreams and a blurred vision of his goals in life. All he had was an undying learning attitude to hold on to. Rowing through ups and downs, it was time that taught him the true meaning of his life.

snippet.title: গোপাল নিজের জন্য একটি দোকান খোলেন | Fun Time With Gopal | Gopal Bhar
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to SONY AATH Channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBz9qbqujcjIavFmBJW2oZw?sub_confirmation=1

Maharaj asks for Gopal when Mantri informs him that Gopal has opened a shop for himself. Mantri tries to instigate Maharaj against Gopal. Maharaj sends a message for Gopal to reach the court ASAP. 

Show Name: Gopal Bhar - গোপালভাঁড়
Directed By : Sourav Mondal, Hansa Mondal
Written By : Hansa Mondal
Original language :  Bengali

#gopalbhar #গোপালভাঁড় #funtimewithgopal 

About the show
-----------------------------
Gopal Bhar was a legendary court jester in medieval Bengal. He was in the court of Raja Krishnachandra, the famous king of Nadia in the 18th century AD. Such was the genius of Gopal that the King considered him a Navaratna of his court. His statue can still be seen in the palace of Raja Krishnachandra. Stories about his exploits are narrated in Bengal to this day and are immortalized in countless short stories. The stories are short, beautiful, humorous, and have a specific social message. Gopal Bhar is famous for stories of his wisdom, in which he outwits other fellow courtiers.

Click to watch all the episodes of Fun Time With Gopal -
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL5O3zv2ZcAShhewEw2H0CqmI2-q-6B19y
